data.text:
The WYLD catalog will be undergoing a scheduled upgrade on August 29, from approximately 8:00 AM to 12:00 PM MST. During this time, the catalog will be in offline mode for about an hour. You will still be able to search for items, but some features like placing holds and renewing checkouts will not be available.
